This dataset contains centerlines representing alley locations. This dataset was originally produced by R and S Digital, Goodland, Kansas. Extensively updated and maintained by the City and County of Denver's GIS Department. Additionally the layer has been joined to Public Works Street Maintenance Alley Inventory to increase value of the layer.</abstract>       <purpose>To digitally and accurately represent the alleys located within the City and County of Denver.</purpose>     </descript>     <status>       <update>As needed</update>     </status>     <spdom>       <bounding>         <westbc>-105.076459</westbc>         <eastbc>-104.735963</eastbc>         <northbc>39.794590</northbc>         <southbc>39.616625</southbc>       </bounding>     </spdom>     <keywords>       <theme>         <themekt>ISO 19115 Topic Categories</themekt>         <themekey>transportation</themekey>       </theme>       <place>         <placekt>None</placekt>         <placekey>Denver</placekey>         <placekey>Denver County</placekey>         <placekey>Colorado</placekey>         <placekey>USA</placekey>       </place>     </keywords>     <accconst>None</accconst>     <useconst>ACCESS CONSTRAINTS:   None.
